PrecisApproval of the variation of the ANNUAL RATE SCALE ORDER, 1994-1995 for the movement of Western grain by rail, made by Order No. 1994-R-233 of the National Transportation Agency, consequential to the "Budget Implementation Act, 1994" which increases the reduction in the government share of freight rates under the Western Grain Transportation Act from 10% to 15% for crop years beginning on or after August 1, 1994.
